        },
        "paragraph_TxyqbN": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "paragraph": "With a portfolio spanning luxury watches, jewellery, fashion, leather goods, accessories, and fragrances, the Group has cultivated longstanding partnerships with some of the world’s most respected luxury brands while establishing itself as a trusted authority within the African luxury market."
          }
        },
        "paragraph_einhiX": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "paragraph": "In 2014, Polo Avenue was launched as the Group’s dedicated luxury fashion subsidiary, created to meet the growing demand for world-class fashion experiences in Africa. Since then, Polo Avenue has become one of Nigeria’s leading multi-brand luxury fashion destinations, curating globally renowned designers alongside emerging contemporary labels for a sophisticated and style-conscious clientele."
          }
